        Senior {siteConfig.jobTitle} / Tech lead
      </div>
      <div class="text-[6pt] mb-3">
        <span>tel: (+34) 654-080-196 |</span>
        <span>email: equero@proton.me |</span>
        <span>github: hbeneke</span>
      </div>
      <div class="text-[9pt] italic">"Never Stop Learning."</div>
    </header>

